column5: There is a 50 hr carp tournament going on right now on the Seneca River in Baldwinsville New York. Here is a look at how it is set up and how it is fished. Carp Tornament Channel 9 news
wow, that is quite the tourney.  Some of the weights on there already are pretty nuts!  Thanks for posting.
Wow thats awesome except for the fishing  weather conditions. I'd love to give that a try but for fun 3 days straight no sleep carp fishing.     karper
No naps allowed ???  I'd miss my naps...

The winners caught over 1000 lbs . Fish under 10 lbs. are not counted. The results of the last two years tournaments have not come close to 3 years ago. The winners that year caught 2800 lbs in total and again fish under 10 lbs don't count.
